Package: clash-config-gen
Version: 1.1.0-1
Depends: libc, coreutils-base64, luci, uhttpd
Source: https://github.com/albawid/ClashConfigGen-OpenWrt
Section: luci
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Albawid <albawid@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Clash Config Generator for OpenWrt (CLI + LuCI UI)
  Convert VMess/VLESS/SS/Trojan proxy URIs to OpenClash YAML.
  Includes LuCI web UI accessible from Services > Clash Config Gen,
  and CLI tool /usr/bin/clash-config-gen for terminal usage.
  Output is copy-paste ready for OpenClash configuration.
